  "body": "<p>Hey there! It’s <a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Zinia</a> back with another fun project using Amy’s amazing Hustle &amp; Heart collection with American Crafts.</p><p>So today I decided to use the beautiful bits of Hustle &amp; Heart in my pocket page diary. Now I guess you are wondering, what on earth is a pocket page diary? Well I really love the project life pocket system but I’m in no way able to keep up with weekly or even monthly spreads. So instead, I use the system like a diary to store my favorite photos, memorabilia, thoughts and pretty much anything you would put in a diary.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595406300864-2645348X2OG74QL22PGM/5a-Zinia-PocketPageDiary-01.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>When it comes to pocket spreads I honestly never have a plan. That sometimes can be a problem but with these beautiful products everything came together effortlessly. First I went through the cut apart sheets and grabbed a few 3x4 and 3x3 cards I liked. Then I started spreading them on my page until I was happy with what I had.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>To turn my 3x3 cards into 3x4s I used some pattern paper scraps and branding strips to add at the top and the bottom to extend their size.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595406374690-FWAUKMMP1L2XJPUBQ0PM/5b-Zinia-PocketPageDiary-02.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I really love using the Hustle &amp; Heart sticker book in pocket page spreads cause they are nice and flat and they don’t add extra bulk in the pockets. On top of that I just love layering them on my photos.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595406410366-SXMSDMMB87LO8Z19O00R/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>To fill in some empty areas, I brought in a few items from the On a Whim collection. Although the color palettes of the two collections are significantly different, they still work beautifully together and they complement each other.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595406426169-M8WH0WVQFP8MKE68MVNU/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Zinia<br/><br/><a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Abstract Inspiration Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abstractinspiration/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbstractInsp\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbstractInspirationPage\">Facebook</a></p><p><strong>SUPPLY LIST:</strong></p><p>378744 ON A WHIM 6x6 PAD | 378746 ON A WHIM THICKERS LOL | 378749 ON A WHIM ACCENT &amp; PHRASE STICKERS | 378735 ON A WHIM 12x12 PAPER - Good Stuff | 376224 OH HAPPY LIFE EPHEMERA | 341861 HUSTLE &amp; HEART 12x12 PAPER - The Little Things | 341863 HUSTLE &amp; HEART 12x12 PAPER - The Right Path | 341864 HUSTLE &amp; HEART 12x12 PAPER - In Alignment | 341869 HUSTLE &amp; HEART 12x12 PAPER - Fit to Be Square | 340878 HUSTLE &amp; HEART 12x12 PAPER - Sweet Sensation | 340877 HUSTLE &amp; HEART 12x12 PAPER - Patchwork Show | 341884 HUSTLE &amp; HEART STICKER BOOK | 341889 HUSTLE &amp; HEART PUFFY HEARTS | 341887 HUSTLE &amp; HEART THICKERS The Lucky Ones</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this adorable minibook, Zinia! Shop HUSTLE &amp; HEART now! Check your local retailer and online at </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/AThustleandheart\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vJOlKd\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
